metadata.analysis_context: Partial statistical analysis of Wisconsin Badgers vs Indiana Hoosiers. This analysis includes only Tasks 4 (Deep Ball Passing & Receiving) and Task 9 (3rd Down & Red Zone Targets) due to limited data availability. All data sourced from CSV exports.
data_quality_notes: This is a PARTIAL analysis - only Tasks 4 and 9 are included
Task 4: Deep Ball Passing & Receiving (20+ air yards) - CSV data only
Task 9: 3rd Down and Red Zone Targets - CSV data only
Tasks 1, 3, 6, 7, 8 are not included (no data available)
All data uses CSV exports exclusively - no API data
Only games present in CSV files are included in totals
metadata.partial_analysis_note: This export contains only 2 of 7 tasks that were completed for the Washington/Wisconsin analysis. The missing tasks (1, 3, 6, 7, 8) require API access or additional CSV files that are not currently available.

task_4.description: Analysis of passing plays with 20 or more air yards downfield, including attempts, completions, yards, touchdowns, and receiving statistics.
task_4.methodology: Data sourced from CSV export. Receiving and passing stats use CSV data exclusively. Only games present in CSV are included.

targets.description: Number of deep ball targets (20+ air yards)

yards.description: Total receiving yards on deep balls

players.description: Player-level breakdown of deep ball receiving stats

task_4.notes: Includes both receiving perspective (targets, receptions, touchdowns) and passing perspective (attempts, completions, interceptions, etc.) data from CSV.

task_9.description: Receiving targets, receptions, first downs, and touchdowns on 3rd down situations and in the Red Zone. Includes player-level breakdown by game.
task_9.methodology: Data sourced from CSV export. All stats (targets, receptions, touchdowns, first downs, yards) use CSV data exclusively. Only games present in CSV are included.

targets.description: Number of targets (3rd down or Red Zone)

receptions.description: Number of receptions (3rd down or Red Zone)

touchdowns.description: Number of touchdowns (3rd down or Red Zone)

first_downs.description: Number of first downs (3rd down or Red Zone)

yards.description: Total receiving yards (3rd down or Red Zone)

task_9.notes: Includes both 3rd down and Red Zone situational targets. Data structure separates 3rd_down and redzone for each team.

data_source_note.receiving_stats: CSV import for receiving targets, receptions, touchdowns, and yards
data_source_note.passing_stats: CSV import for passing attempts, completions, touchdowns, yards, interceptions, and other passing metrics
data_source_note.note: Receiving and passing stats use CSV data EXCLUSIVELY. Only games present in CSV are included.
CSV import for all 3rd down and Red Zone stats (targets, receptions, touchdowns, first downs, yards)
data_source_note.note_detail: 3rd down and Red Zone targets data uses CSV data EXCLUSIVELY. Only games present in CSV are included.
